            href="https://www.goodreads.com/series/117100-red-rising-saga"
            rel="noreffer nofollow"
            target="_blank">Red Rising</a
          > saga, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/series/135117-the-cosmere" rel="noreffer nofollow" target="_blank"
