          >, and <a
            href="https://www.goodreads.com/series/45262-the-kingkiller-chronicle"
            rel="noreffer nofollow"
            target="_blank">The Kingkiller Chronicle</a
          >. (Ask me about my favorite moments — I’ve got opinions.)
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether I’m building software or hitting the trail, I bring the same passion, focus, and curiosity to
          everything I do.
        </p>
